channel.title: Need help with ::vote command , webclient:( could someone please help me out
channel.description:
Hi guys, 3 days ago i made my new server called klik-hier-scape. since we do not have a webclient and not very much votes we do not have much players yet. i was wondering if someone could help me out by making a webclient for me, and a ::vote command. We could use teamviewer
Hope someone will be so nice to help me :)
greetz ;)
